    <item>
      <title>感谢私募股权的寿司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-06/thank-private-equity-for-your-sushi-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对寿司的需求在美国增长。彭博的Dani Burger参观了Baja Aqua Farms，这是Sashimi-Grade Tuna的顶级生产商之一，探讨了金枪鱼的耕种方式和太平洋蓝鳍金枪鱼的独特模型。我们与Equity Group Investments的Mark Sotir坐下来，了解私募股权在金枪鱼中看到的机会。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-06/thank-private-equity-for-your-sushi-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 12:08:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>令人惊讶的输出越来越大之后，沙特阿拉斯州的石油价格削减了亚洲的油价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/saudis-slash-oil-prices-for-asia-days-after-surprise-output-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧佩克+联盟宣布出乎意料的大型输出飙升之后的几天，沙特阿拉伯在两年多以上的旗舰石油价格上涨了最多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/saudis-slash-oil-prices-for-asia-days-after-surprise-output-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 11:41:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾将卖空规则收紧到平静的市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/taiwan-tightens-short-selling-rules-to-calm-market-amid-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾的金融监管机构宣布，在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的积极关税中，稳定市场的销量更严格，以稳定市场。]]></description>
