    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚向奈拉避免关税后果提供美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/nigeria-supplies-dollars-to-shield-naira-from-tariff-fallout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚的中央银行将美元卖给了贷方，以阻止奈拉汇率的侵蚀，这是在美国关税动荡引起的抛售后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/nigeria-supplies-dollars-to-shield-naira-from-tariff-fallout</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 09:32:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度专注于贸易协议，避免对美国关税进行报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/india-to-focus-on-trade-deal-avoids-retaliation-on-us-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度一位印度政府官员说，印度不太可能立即对唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税征收，并将努力集中在与美国达成双边贸易协定方面，以降落职责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/india-to-focus-on-trade-deal-avoids-retaliation-on-us-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 09:25:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东股票，Aramco沉没在关税，石油的双重威胁上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/mideast-stocks-suffer-worst-rout-since-2020-on-oil-tariff-shock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[包括沙特阿拉伯在内的中东国家的主要股票基准沉没在2020年以来，这是投资者对全球贸易战争和石油价格低迷的风险的反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/mideast-stocks-suffer-worst-rout-since-2020-on-oil-tariff-shock</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 08:08:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国投资者周一对美国关税报复的“丑陋”付出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/china-investors-brace-for-ugly-monday-on-us-tariff-retaliation</link>
